  m_text: "<size=125%><b><color=#7BE8FF>LEVEL 1: CONVERSIE BINAR -> ZECIMAL</color></b></size>\r\n\r\n\xCEn
    binar folosim doar <b>0</b> \u0219i <b>1</b>.\r\nFiecare pozi\u021Bie are o valoare:\r\n<b>1
    | 2 | 4 | 8</b>\r\n\r\nAdun\u0103 doar valorile unde apare <b>1</b>.\r\n\r\nExemplu:\r\n<b>0101
    = 4 + 1 = 5</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Cerin\u021B\u0103:</b> apas\u0103 pe cuburi p\xE2n\u0103
    ob\u021Bii valoarea cerut\u0103.\r\n\r\n<size=65%><color=#A0A0A0>Apas\u0103 click
    pentru a \xEEnchide.</color></size>\r\n"
